  "texts": [
    "We only retained studies with full texts in English and focused exclusively on empirical studies, excluding editorials, commentaries, and position papers.",
    "Given that question generation has applications in other domains like chatbots and customer service, we confined our selection to studies in the education field.",
    "This focus was achieved by identifying education-related words or phrases in the title, abstracts, or keywords.",
    "Additionally, we selected publications that focused on item generation, excluding other forms of text generation, such as the creation of reading passages without items generated.",
    "After the initial screening, we noted 47 disagreements in selection decisions, resulting in a high agreement rate of 93.44%."
  ],
